                  <Text layoutX="26.0" layoutY="23.0" strokeType="OUTSIDE" strokeWidth="0.0" text="Welcome to Quizzzzz!&#10;&#10;This page teaches you how to play the game.&#10;&#10;&#10;==== Choosing a username and a server ====&#10;&#10;First things first, you should choose the username that you will use during the game, you can do that on the first page.&#10;The next thing you should do is enter the ip of the server you want to connect to, you can leave it blank to&#10;use your own ip.&#10;&#10;&#10;==== Starting a game ====&#10;&#10;Once your username and ip are set, you will get access to the game page.&#10;On this page you can choose to start a singleplayer game or a multiplayer game, you can also access the leaderboard&#10;and the admin panel which will be covered later.&#10;&#10;&#10;==== Singleplayer game ====&#10;&#10;In the case that you chose to start a singleplayer game,  you will immediately start a new game.&#10;&#10;The game features 3 question types:&#10;- &quot;What uses the most energy&quot;&#10;==&gt; you will be shown three answers, click on the correct one.&#10;- &quot;Instead of x you can do y&quot;&#10;==&gt; you will also be shown three answers, click on the correct one.&#10;- &quot;How much energy does x takes&quot;&#10;==&gt; you will be asked to input a number, you should enter your best &#10;&#10;In this mode, you have access to two jokers that you can each use one time in a game.&#10;The first joker removes one of the three possible answers you are presented with, user it when you're not sure about&#10;an answer.&#10;The second joker doubles your points for the current round, use it when you're really sure that you have the right&#10;answer.&#10;&#10;&#10;==== Multiplayer game ====&#10;&#10;In the case that you chose to start a multiplayer game, you will be sent to a lobby where you can wait for&#10;other users to join.&#10;When enough users have joined the lobby, click on &quot;Start Game&quot; to launch the game.&#10;&#10;The questions in this game mode are similar to the singleplayer mode.&#10;&#10;In this mode, you have access to the same jokers as the singleplayer mode.&#10;You can also use a third joker, which halves the remaining time of all players.&#10;&#10;&#10;==== Leaderboard ====&#10;&#10;Once you're in the game start screen, you will have access to the public singleplayer leaderboard.&#10;It displays the best scores that users got in the singleplayer game.&#10;&#10;&#10;==== Admin pannel ====&#10;&#10;In the game start screen, you also have access to the administrator pannel.&#10;Here you can check which activities are stored in your own database, you can also import new activities.&#10;These are the activities that will show up in games hosted on your own server.">
